name: Coded (A Misinterpretation)
description: An abstract sci-fi digital collage! Beneath many things in our lives is an underlying code, giving new meaning to old things, hiding intentions, or even controlling the masses. Subliminal messages are no myth & is practically inescapable in modern times. I find this concept to be interesting & seek to further explore it as a medium. There is no underlying code in this image, but I'm curious what viewing it makes you think about, & why we are coded to think certain ways.
